---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import TimeLineElement from "../components/cv/TimeLine.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Resume">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Profile</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10 text-justify">
    Software engineer with ability to learn and collaborate in rapidly changing
    environments and compositions. <br /> Always try to get the job done a better
    way. That's why I use neovim, tmux and shell scripting in my dev workflow. <br
    />Falling love with suckless philosophy and wanna write more about it (both
    blogging and programming).
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Education</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container grid gap-4 mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="B.A. Computer Science"
      subtitle="From 2018 to 2022 at VNUHCM - University of Science, Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Experience</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Blockchain Developer (smart contract mainly)"
      subtitle="From 2022 at Beowulf Blockchain, Vietnam"
      desc="Research, build, deploy smart contracts to different networks | Backend Developer"
    />
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Mobile Freelancer"
      subtitle="From 2019 to 2021 at Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam"
      desc=".NET Framework | Mobile developer | Automation tool with Selenium"
    />
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Self-taught programming"
      subtitle="From 2017 to 2018 at High school"
      desc="Mobile App development using Android (Java). And some cool stuff like Arduino and Linux."
    />
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Certifications</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-10 grid gap-2">
    <li>
      <a href="https://www.efset.org/cert/DxtNKG" target="_blank">
        EF SET English Certificate 74/100 (C2 Proficient)</a
      >
    </li>
    <li>
      <a
        href="https://certiprof.com/pages/scrum-foundation-professional-certificate-sfpc-en-sp"
        target="_blank"
      >
        Scrum Foundation Professional Certificate (SFPC)</a
      >
    </li>
  </ul>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Skills</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc md:columns-4 columns-2 mb-10 mx-6">
    <!--- 
        col1: Programming languages
        col2: DBMS
        col3: Architecture
        col4: Framework
        col5: Tools
        -->
    <li>Rust (Most loved)</li>
    <li>JavaScript/TypeScript</li>
    <li>Node.js</li>
    <li>Golang</li>
    <li>Solidity</li>
    <li>C/C++</li>
    <li>Scripting languages: Python, Shell, Lua</li>
    <li>C# (WPF, Xamarin)</li>
    <li>Linux</li>
    <li>MongoDB</li>
    <li>Postgres SQL</li>
    <li>MySQL</li>
    <li>Clickhouse</li>
    <li>.NET Framework (ASP.NET MVC)</li>
    <li>Entity Framework</li>
    <li>MVC & MVVM</li>
    <li>Express.js</li>
    <li>Selenium</li>
    <li>Astro (this page ^^)</li>
    <li>Git</li>
    <li>Neovim</li>
    <li>Scrum</li>
    <li>Data Structure & Algorithms</li>
    <li>Design Pattern</li>
    <li>Distributed System</li>
    <li>Blockchain</li>
    <li>Cryptography</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Projects</div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
